summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North Fifty-fifth Street from East Green Lake Boulevard to Keystone Place et al in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing under Ordinance No. 15077, creating Local Improvement District No. 1369 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
